data.description: Charming 2-story home in Tomball, boasting 2300 sqft of well-maintained living space. This delightful residence, built in 2006, is situated in a small and welcoming community. Zoned to the prestigious Klein Independent School District, it offers an ideal educational environment for families. Step inside to discover a recently painted interior, creating a fresh and inviting atmosphere. The entire second floor is adorned with new carpeting, adding a touch of modern comfort to each room. The layout is thoughtfully designed, offering a cozy ambiance while still catering to the needs of growing needs. Only minutes from Grand Parkway, Tomball Parkway, and lots of shopping and dining in close proximity. Enjoy the small town feel of Tomball, with local events every weekend! Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming 2-story house your home. With its recent updates, ideal location, and friendly design, it's a residence that combines practicality with a touch of charm.
